metatags.og:description:
72 likes, 2 comments - thorntonmartialarts on April 16, 2025: "The Journey Continues!

Our next Muaythai Development League (MDL) event is coming up on Sunday, June 22nd in Connecticut!

This is the perfect opportunity for kids, teens, and adults (ages 6 and up) to test their skills, build confidence, and grow as martial artists in a safe, structured, and supportive environment.

The MDL isn’t just about competition — it’s about development. Athletes of all levels come to sharpen their craft, gain experience, and embrace the true spirit of Muay Thai through semi-contact technical sparring.

Whether you’re a new athlete eager to step onto the mat or a coach looking to prepare your students, this is the place to be.

Registration is now open!
Link in bio.".
